cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL

The paper deals with transfer learning in computer vision using deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a transfer module that assigns weights to features extracted from pre-trained models, which is related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper incorporates an auxiliary classifier as an extra regularizer, which is related to neural networks and computational linguistics (cs.NE and cs.CL).
